{{Top|leg}}
The '''Coruscant Star of Valor''' was one of the first medals that was issued by the [[New Republic/Legends|New Republic]],<ref name="TCSWE">''[[The Complete Star Wars Encyclopedia]]''</ref> first struck in [[7 ABY/Legends|7 ABY]]. It commemorated the participants of the [[Liberation of Coruscant (Galactic Civil War)|Seizure of Coruscant]]<ref name="TCSWE" /> and was declared to be the highest honor that could be given for valor by the developing government.

The first recipients of the award were the members of [[Rogue Squadron/Legends|Rogue Squadron]], which included [[Asyr Sei'lar]].

